data.description: Welcome home to this inviting, open, functional floor plan with abundant natural light from its many captivating windows on 2 acres!!  Upon entering, you are greeted with a unique entryway, family/dining area, around the corner features 3 bedrooms/2 bathrooms. Then into the deluxe central kitchen with breakfast bar boasting an ample amount of counter space, woodstove, & utility area. Next you will enter into a huge family room, your own spa room oriented to view Squaw Butte. Downstairs you will find a cellar style pantry, separate living space including 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, kitchen & living space. Walk out to the fenced yard with sidewalks leading into a huge storage area. Home has an attached 2 car garage, enormous shop w/ wood stove, tons of parking, room to roam inside and out!!
